---
title: Black Bean & Sweet Potato Bake with Feta, Jalapeño, and Tomato Salad
description: Nutrient-packed black beans and sweet potato make for a hearty Mexican-inspired skillet bake. A few minutes under the broiler melts the feta just enough to make it creamy and delicious.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56fa89524dab713d278b4567.jpg
